anberry%20soda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20everything%20was%20different.%20The%20old%20classic%20dishes%20didn't%20offer%20the%20culinary%20homecoming%20I'd%20been%20hoping%20for.%20Instead%2C%20I%20got%20horrid%20stomach%20cramps%20and%20acute%20nausea.%20The%20Buffalo%20wing%20mythology%20no%20longer%20held%20up.%20More%20importantly%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f11ff5ba-994d-403e-a6e0-5b3d637957f9%5C%22%3EMy%20%26quot%3B6-month%26quot%3B%20journey%20to%20Thailand%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20breaking%20up%20with%20my%20long-term%20boyfriend%2C%20crashing%20my%20car%2C%20and%20quitting%20my%20job%20%E2%80%94%20in%20that%20order%20%E2%80%94%20I%20moved%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-lotus-season-3-hotel-location-thailand-resort-four-seasons-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKoh%20Samui%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20told%20everyone%20I'd%20be%20back%20in%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20six%20months%20passed%20on%20the%20tropical%20island%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Thailand%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20heading%20home%2C%20I%20made%20a%20visa%20run%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flao-china-railway-train-ride-countryside-burned-photos-laos-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThai-Laos%20border%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20stay%20for%20longer.%20It%20would%20be%20my%20first%20of%20many%2C%20extending%20my%20initial%20six%20months%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20hooked%20on%20the%20steamy%20weather%2C%20the%20beaches%20with%20water%20the%20color%20of%20blue%20topaz%2C%20and%20the%20food.%20The%20ice-cold%20pineapples%20tasted%20as%20sweet%20as%20sponge%20candy%20(a%20treat%20from%20Buffalo%20similar%20to%20toffee).%20Lunch%20usually%20included%20spicy%20som%20tom%20with%20sour%20tamarind%2C%20peanuts%2C%20and%20shrimp%2C%20along%20with%20coconut%20water%20straight%20from%20the%20shell%20%E2%80%94%20always%20served%20with%20a%20little%20spoon%20to%20dig%20out%20the%20creamy%20flesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFresh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjay-fai-michelin-star-bangkok-street-food-stall-review-price-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThai%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20tropical%20climate%20did%20come%20with%20a%20few%20tradeoffs.%20Spiders%2C%20as%20big%20as%20softballs%2C%20would%20plop%20in%20front%20of%20me%20and%20scuttle%20away%20to%20some%20dark%20corner%20of%20my%20bathroom%20as%20I%20shrieked%20and%20swatted%20to%20no%20avail.%20Cockroaches%20were%20similarly%20supersized%2C%20and%20some%20could%20fly.%20Packs%20of%20stray%20dogs%20and%20lumbering%20monitor%20lizards%20shared%20urban%20space%2C%20even%20taking%20refuge%20in%20air-conditioned%207-11s%20during%20the%20most%20sweltering%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsleeper-train-thailand-overnight-booking-tickets-guide-bangkok-chiang-mai-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThai%20transportation%3C%2Fa%3E%20wasn't%20always%20reliable%20or%20safe%2C%20including%20rickety%20trains%20that%20often%20ran%20late.%20Sometimes%20you'd%20hear%20horror%20stories%20about%20them%20derailing.%20Once%2C%20I%20heard%20an%20unsubstantiated%20and%20harrowing%20rumor%20about%20a%20monkey%20that%20climbed%20up%20a%20train%20toilet%20and%20terrorized%20the%20passengers%20until%20someone%20tranquilized%20it.%20While%20this%20particular%20story%20might%20be%20a%20total%20myth%2C%20anyone%20who's%20ever%20ridden%20those%20trains%20knows%20that%20a%20stowaway%20is%20not%20entirely%20implausible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233c2ad4b-39eb-4691-95dd-015aec9d3537%5C%22%3EA%20strange%20homecoming%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-abroad-thailand-cheaper-respectful-retiree-resort-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyears%20in%20Thailand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20come%20home.%20I%20missed%20reliable%20transportation%2C%20manageable%20bugs%2C%20the%20change%20of%20seasons%2C%20my%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20and%20the%20Great%20Lakes%20comfort%20food%20I'd%20been%20pining%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20relished%20the%20change.%20Buffalo%20is%20gloriously%20predictable%20in%20the%20best%20possible%20way.%20There%20are%20no%20surprise%20toilet%20monkeys.%20The%20trains%20do%20not%20derail.%20The%20food%20delivers%20on%20its%20promises%3A%20fatty%2C%20spicy%2C%20bready%2C%20and%20often%20served%20with%20a%20big%20cup%20of%20chunky%20blue%20cheese.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20is%20not%20much%20public%20transportation%2C%20and%20as%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20car%2C%20I%20was%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20Uber.%20Also%2C%20my%20tastebuds%20had%20veered%20sharply%20from%20the%20local%20cuisine%20during%20my%20years%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20catching%20up%20with%20family%20and%20old%20friends%2C%20I%20felt%20little%20connection%20to%20my%20hometown.%20It%20was%20jarring%2C%20unexpected%2C%20and%20deeply%20sad.%20After%20three%20years%20away%2C%20my%20happy%20homecoming%20felt%20more%20like%20visiting%20a%20distant%20place%20full%20of%20friendly%20and%20familiar%20faces%20than%20settling%20back%20into%20my%20comfort%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20even%20realized%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomfort-food-around-the-world-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefinition%20of%20comfort%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22631%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blonde%20woman%20looking%20off%20to%20the%20sunset%20from%20a%20boat%20in%20Costa%20Rica%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643105e9686a6f37bff8fbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22469%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%20a%20year%20back%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20author%20moved%20south%20to%20Costa%20Rica%3Cp%3EEli