%2Fman-with-knife-wounds-several-in-swiss-town-police%2Farticleshow%2F110157862.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fman-with-knife-wounds-several-in-swiss-town-police%2Famp_articleshow%2F110157862.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fman-with-knife-wounds-several-in-swiss-town-police%2Famp_articleshow%2F110157862.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waymo%2C%20the%20self-driving%20car%20company%20owned%20by%20Google's%20parent%2C%20Alphabet%3A%20How%20to%20ride%2C%20cost%2C%20accident%20record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223731%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%2C%20self-driving%20Waymo%20car%20sits%20parked%20in%20a%20San%20Francisco%20street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d81d161f51cc001968684b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222483%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaymo%20is%20Alphabet's%20robotaxi%20service%20currently%20operating%20in%20multiple%20US%20cities%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20launch%20in%20more.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWaymo%20is%20Alphabet's%20robotaxi%20service%20formerly%20known%20as%20the%20Google%20Self-Driving%20Car%20Project.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWaymo's%20driverless%20taxis%20are%20currently%20operating%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELike%20its%20main%20competitor%2C%20Cruise%2C%20Waymo's%20autonomous%20vehicles%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20accidents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20is%20a%20robotaxi%20service%20owned%20by%20Google's%20parent%20company%2C%20Alphabet%20Inc.%20It%20was%20initially%20formed%20by%20Google%20and%20known%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-car-project-history-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Self-Driving%20Car%20Project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20following%20seven%20years%20of%20research%20and%20development%20before%20eventually%20being%20spun%20out%20to%20its%20own%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20started%20developing%20Waymo%20and%20its%20self-driving%20technology%20in%202009%20at%20the%20Google%20X%20lab%2C%20which%20was%20led%20by%20Google%20co-founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsergey-brin-career-life-education%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESergey%20Brin%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20almost%20two%20years%20of%20testing%20the%20technology%2C%20Google%20and%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20revealed%20its%20existence%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20lawmakers%20raised%20concerns%20at%20the%20time%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20regulations%20for%20this%20new%20technological%20front.%20Google%20was%20a%20prominent%20supporter%2C%20lobbying%20for%20regulation.%20By%202012%2C%20Nevada's%20Department%20of%20Motor%20Vehicles%20had%20licensed%20a%20self-driving%20Prius%20running%20Google's%20software.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20self-driving%20vehicle%20was%20licensed%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Alphabet%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsundar-pichai-google-alphabet-ceo-career-life%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESundar%20Pichai%3C%2Fa%3E%20distanced%20Waymo%20and%20Alphabet's%20other%20subsidiaries%20from%20Google%20by%20granting%20them%20more%20autonomy%20to%20design%20job%20structures%20and%20compensations%20outside%20of%20Google's%20job%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20has%20been%20impacted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-layoffs-more-employees-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%3A%20The%20company%20cut%20roughly%208%25%20of%20Waymo's%20staff%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20restructuring%2C%20Waymo's%20offices%20are%20still%20located%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California%2C%20just%20a%20short%20drive%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogleplex-google-headquarters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogleplex%2C%20Google's%20global%20headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223a20b05b-219f-45c4-b07e-359adaec4499%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20Waymo%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20a%20Waymo%20driverless%20taxi%20is%20shown%20navigating%20down%20a%20Los%20Angeles%20street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66197fe71caec1275a6fb5bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaymo%20first%20began%20publicly%20operating%20in%20Phoenix%20in%202020.%20Its%20services%20are%20waitlisted%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20provides%20driverless%20taxi%20services%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20Phoenix%2C%20using%20its%20fleet%20of%20autonomous%20vehicles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Google%20was%20granted%20a%20patent%20for%20a%20transportation%20service%20involving%20automated%20vehicles%20that%20would%20be%20funded%20by%20advertising%20fees.%20That%20May%2C%20Google%20unveiled%20a%20prototype%20autonomous%20vehicle%20that%20did%20not%20contain%20a%20gas%20pedal%2C%20brake%20pedal%2C%20or%20steering%20wheel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20they%20gave%20their%20first%20fully%20autonomous%20ride%20to%20a%20legally%20blind%20friend%20of%20principal%20engineer%20Nathaniel%20Fairfield%3B%20unlike%20earlier%20tests%2C%20there%20was%20no%20police%20escort%2C%20no%20test%20driver%2C%20and%20it%20was%20not%20on%20a%20closed%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20this%20self-driving%20car%20project%20was%20spun%20out%20of%20Google%20and%20made%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-alphabet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20parent%20company%2C%20Alphabet%3C%2Fa%3E%20Inc.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20the%20company%20also%20ordered%20100%20Chrysler%20Pacifica%20hybrid%20minivans%20to%20test%20the%20technology.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20reduce%20manufacturing%20costs%20by%2090%25%20and%20partnered%20with%20other%20auto%20manufacturers%20and%20the%20ridesharing%20service%20Lyft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20started%20its%20public%20operations%20in%20Phoenix%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a5c26ca7-5210-4c02-94ce-9523184d352b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20can%20take%20a%20Waymo%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Waymo%20only%20operates%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20but%20is%20set%20to%20launch%20in%20Austin%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProspective%20riders%20can%20sign%20up%20to%20the%20company's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwaymo.com%2Fwaymo-one%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaymo%20One%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20downloading%20the%20Waymo%20One%20app%20from%20either%20Google%20Play%20or%20the%20iOS%20App%20Store.%20Waymo%20is%20currently%20widely%20available%20to%20the%20public%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20but%20services%20are%20waitlisted%20for%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20and%20Austin.%20Like%20major%20competitors%2C%20prospective%20riders%20are%20quoted%20the%20fare%20while%20booking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaymo%20ride%20prices%20are%20based%20on%20the%20distance%20and%20time%20of%20a%20trip%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20minimum%20price%20charged%20for%20all%20trips.%20In%20April%20of%202023%2C%20when%20a%20Business%20Insider%20reporter%20tested%20the%20technology%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20a%20five-mile%2C%2020-minute%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frode-self-driving-waymo-car-phoenix-and-wasnt-scary-review-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaymo%20ride%20cost%20%2411%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20same%20price%20as%20an%20Uber%20trip%20to%20the%20same%20location.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223d6e0a6-8d5e-4acd-8e06-ef4120f9ac2a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaymo%20has%20had%20multiple%20accidents%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20any%20new%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20indeed%2C%20any%20motor%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20mishaps%20can%20be%20expected.%20In%20February%202024%2C%20Waymo%20voluntarily%20recalled%20and%20updated%20its%20robotaxi%20software%20after%20two%20of%20its%20autonomous%20vehicles%20crashed%20into%20the%20same%20towed%20pickup%20truck%20in%20Phoenix.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20string%20of%20incidents%20over%20the%20prior%20weeks%2C%20affecting%20more%20than%20one%20company.%20A%20couple%20of%20weeks%20earlier%2C%20a%20Waymo%20vehicle%20non-fatally%20struck%20a%20cyclist%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20rival%20Cruise%20suspended%20operations%20following%20an%20October%20crash%20that%20struck%20and%20dragged%20a%20pedestrian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715810161000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66198f4f16bde8d4ead88db2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Waymo%20was%20previously%20known%20as%20the%20Google%20Self-Driving%20Car%20Project.%20Alphabet's%20robotaxi%20service%20now%20offers%20rides%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20LA.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kyle%40ktwilson.ca%20(Kyle%20Wilson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20stopped%20saving%20much%20for%20retirement%20when%20my%20husband%20died%2C%20and%20I've%20found%203%20more%20important%20things%20to%20spend%20that%20money%20on%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-saving-for-retirement-spending-my-money-other-things-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaid%20non-client%20promotion%3A%20Affiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting-rating-methodology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20investing%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22writer%20allison%20nichol%20longtin%20and%20her%20late%20husband%20are%20photographed%20outdoors%20in%20front%20of%20a%20lake%20on%20their%20wedding%20day%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F617069e7fee39f0018fa8266%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221944%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20left%2C%20with%20her%20late%20husband.%3Cp%3EAllison%20Nichol%20Longtin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20died%20when%20I%20was%2031%3B%20we'd%20been%20diligently%20saving%20for%20retirement.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20regret%20not%20spending%20more%20of%20our%20earnings%20on%20experiences%20and%20things%20we%20would%20have%20enjoyed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20widow%2C%20I'm%20spending%20on%20my%20home%20and%20mobility%20instead%20of%20saving%20for%20a%20future%20that's%20not%20promised.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20out%20there%20to%20save%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fretirement%5C%22%3Eretirement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20buying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20in%20financial%20literacy%20and%20practice%20sound%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-budget%5C%22%3Emoney%20management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20this%20is%20one%20piece%20of%20financial%20advice%20that%20I'm%20ignoring%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%20I'm%2036%20years%20old.%20I%20was%2031%20when%20I%20became%20a%20widow.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20had%20been%20diligently%20putting%20money%20aside%20for%20our%20retirement%20when%20he%20died%20suddenly%20in%202017%20and%20my%20whole%20world%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20rule%2C%20I%20don't%20waste%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20on%20regrets%20and%20things%20I%20can't%20change%2C%20but%20I%20do%20regret%20that%2C%20as%20a%20couple%2C%20we%20didn't%20spend%20more%20of%20our%20hard-earned%20money%20on%20experiences%20and%20things%20that%20could%20have%20improved%20our%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20like%20taking%20that%20long-anticipated%20and%20partially%20planned%20hiking%20holiday%20in%20Iceland%20or%20moving%20to%20a%20more%20spacious%20apartment%20on%20a%20quieter%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELosing%20my%20husband%20changed%20my%20perspective%20on%20spending%20and%20saving%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20life%2C%20I%20observed%20my%20dad's%20sometimes%20extremely%20frugal%20ways%20and%20internalized%20a%20waste-not-want-not%20mentality.%20In%20my%2020s%2C%20I%20married%20a%20man%20who%20was%20cautious%20with%20money%20and%20favored%20saving%20and%20investing%20over%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20many%20hard-won%20lessons%20from%20his%20unexpected%20death%2C%20I%20learned%20to%20focus%20more%20fully%20on%20the%20present%2C%20which%20has%20affected%20how%20I%20manage%20my%20finances.%20In%20my%2030s%2C%20I'm%20actively%20working%20to%20balance%20saving%20for%20my%20future%20with%20enjoying%20the%20fruits%20of%20my%20labor%20now%20while%20I%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20modest%20RRSP%20(Registered%20Retirement%20Savings%20Plan)%2C%20which%20I%20contribute%20to%20every%20so%20often%2C%20but%20it's%20far%20from%20my%20main%20financial%20focus.%20I%20hear%20some%20of%20you%20out%20there%20gasping%20at%20what%20may%20sound%20like%20a%20flippant%20attitude%20toward%20planning%20for%20my%20financial%20future.%20It's%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI'm%20saving%20for%203%20things%20I%20care%20about%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20I'm%20putting%20money%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Esavings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20home%20repairs%20and%20odd%20jobs%20around%20the%20house%2C%20driving%20lessons%20and%20a%20car%2C%20and%20a%20gravel%20bike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home-repair%20savings%20help%20me%20sleep%20at%20night%20in%20my%20century-old%20home%20that%20I%20bought%20in%202020%20and%20have%20been%20loving%20back%20to%20its%20former%20glory%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20driving%20lessons%20and%20eventual%20car%20represent%20new%20learning%2C%20increased%20independence%2C%20and%20moving%20forward%20in%20my%20life.%20Yes%2C%20I'm%20a%2036-year-old%20who's%20never%20learned%20to%20drive.%20I've%20always%20lived%20in%20cities%20where%20driving%20would%20have%20been%20more%20of%20a%20headache%20or%20a%20nice-to-have%20than%20a%20need.%20I%20left%20the%20city%20for%20small-town%20life%20to%20buy%20my%20first%20home%20and%20dream%20of%20buying%20a%20rural%20country%20property%20with%20land%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20A%20car%20is%20essential%20to%20that%20dream%20and%20not%20having%20one%20or%20being%20able%20to%20drive%20is%20already%20cramping%20my%20lifestyle%20in%20my%20new%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gravel%20bike%20represents%20fun%20and%20freedom.%20It%20is%20an%20attainable%20financial%20goal%20that%20will%20be%20a%20tangible%20reminder%20of%20my%20hard%20work%20and%20hopefully%20tide%20me%20over%20until%20I%20have%20my%20driver's%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepriving%20myself%20of%20these%20things%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20putting%20aside%20money%20for%20a%20future%20retirement%20that%20may%20never%20come%20or%20that%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20feels%20too%20far%20off%20to%20be%20real%2C%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20to%20me%20right%20now.%20This%20may%20sound%20maudlin%20or%20overly%20dramatic%2C%20but%20I've%20lived%20it%2C%20I%20%3Cem%3Eam%20living%20it%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20Tomorrow%20is%20never%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGet%20Exclusive%20Savings%20with%20Raisin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Open%20a%20no-fee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fraisin-review%5C%22%3ERaisin%3C%2Fa%3E%20account%20in%20minutes%20and%20spread%20your%20savings%20across%20an%20exclusive%20network%20of%20over%2030%20FDIC-insured%20banks%20and%20NCUA-insured%20credit%20unions.%20Earn%20top%20savings%20rates%20and%20manage%20it%20all%20with%20a%20single%20secure%20login.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20prioritize%20the%20life%20I'm%20living%20right%20now%20over%20a%20future%20that%20isn't%20promised%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20freelancer%20with%20my%20own%20business.%20I%20work%20very%20hard%20and%20I%20don't%20play%20enough.%20I'm%20working%20on%20that%2C%20too.%20I'm%20coming%20around%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20I%20deserve%20to%20enjoy%20my%20money.%20Not%20least%20of%20all%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20the%20life%20I%20thought%20I%20would%3A%20I've%20lost%20my%20husband%2C%20the%20children%20we%20planned%20to%20have%2C%20and%20the%20house%20in%20the%20city%20we%20saved%20up%20to%20buy%2C%20all%20in%20one%20horrible%20instant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20use%20this%20tragic%20loss%20to%20justify%20reckless%20spending.%20Rather%2C%20it's%20a%20lens%20I%20use%20to%20bring%20into%20greater%20focus%20the%20choices%20I%20make%2C%20both%20financially%20and%20in%20other%20areas%20of%20my%20life.%20I've%20loved%20and%20been%20loved%20deeply%20and%20I've%20lost%20profoundly.%20And%2C%20I'm%20still%20here.%20I'm%20working%20to%20rebuild%20my%20life.%20I'm%20adjusting%20my%20financial%20goals%20and%20behaviors%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20tax%20season%20approaches%20and%20the%20messages%20urging%20all%20of%20us%20to%20contribute%20to%20retirement%20planning%20start%20to%20circulate%2C%20momentum%20building%20toward%20the%20deadline%2C%20a%20noisy%2C%20ticking%20pressure-filled%20clock%2C%20I%20tune%20it%20all%20out.%20When%20I%20feel%20myself%20buckling%20under%20the%20pressure%2C%20I%20call%20to%20mind%20what%20my%20wise%20and%20wonderful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3Efinancial%20planner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Liz%2C%20once%20told%20me%20during%20our%20first%20session%20after%20I%20bought%20my%20first%20home%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20live%20in%20your%20biggest%20investment%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20it's%20your%20retirement%20fund%2C%20especially%20once%20the%20house%20is%20paid%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20I%20didn't%20contribute%20to%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%3Eretirement%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20nor%20did%20I%20the%20year%20before%20that.%20If%20I%20have%20a%20particularly%20good%20year%20this%20year%2C%20I%20may%20well%20contribute%2C%20but%20it%20won't%20be%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20doing%20the%20things%20that%20make%20my%20life%20full%20right%20now.%20I've%20learned%20that%20life%20is%20short%20and%20I%20want%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20experiences%20and%20things%20I%20can%20enjoy%20now%2C%20but%20that%