EThe%20move%20is%20a%20major%20step%20for%20the%20allies%20toward%20defending%20against%20new%20missile%20threats%20from%20China%20and%20others.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20Japan%20have%20agreed%20to%20work%20together%20to%20develop%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuge-air-battles-show-us-needs-most-missile-war-china-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefense%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20defeat%20hypersonic%20missiles%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defense.gov%2FNews%2FReleases%2FRelease%2FArticle%2F3775546%2Fus-department-of-defense-statement-on-the-signing-of-the-glide-phase-intercepto%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHypersonic%20missiles%20are%20a%20daunting%20challenge%20and%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20current%20missile-defense%20systems%20to%20stop%20because%20they%20can%20fly%20low%20and%20maneuver%20along%20unpredictable%20flight%20paths%2C%20making%20the%20new%20project%20the%20US%20and%20Japan%20are%20working%20on%20significant%20as%20the%20two%20allies%20face%20emerging%20Russian%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-military-china-missile-problem-getting-worse-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChinese%20missile%20threats%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Japan%20%26quot%3Bfinalized%20a%20formal%20agreement%20for%20a%20Glide%20Phase%20Interceptor%20(GPI)%20Cooperative%20Development%20(GCD)%20Project%20Arrangement%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20aims%20to%20develop%20a%20missile%20defense%20system%20that%20can%20effectively%20intercept%20hypersonic%20weapons%20in%20the%20glide%20phase%20of%20their%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20bilateral%20agreement%20is%20the%20culmination%20of%20over%20a%20year%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20Plans%20for%20the%20co-development%20of%20a%20GPI%20were%20originally%20announced%20in%20August%202023%20during%20a%20Japan-US%20summit.%20The%20US%20Missile%20Defense%20Agency%20will%20lead%20the%20development%20of%20the%20GPI%2C%20while%20Japan%20will%20contribute%20specific%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20joint%20statement%2C%20the%20allies%20said%20that%20the%20coming%20%26quot%3BGPI%20will%20deliver%20a%20regional%20defensive%20capability%20over%20time%20as%20part%20of%20a%20holistic%20layered%20defensive%20architecture.%20The%20GPI%20co-development%20will%20build%20upon%20long-standing%20U.S.-Japan%20missile%20defense%20cooperation%20and%20strengthen%20the%20Alliance%20deterrence%20posture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20navy%20frigate%20Admiral%20Gorshkov%20and%20a%20Zircon%20hypersonic%20missile%20in%20White%20Sea%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cb46b0f533b039a882c7f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20navy%20frigate%20Admiral%20Gorshkov%20launching%20a%20Zircon%20hypersonic%20missile%20in%20White%20Sea%2C%20Russia%2C%20on%20July%2019%2C%202021.%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20via%20AP%2C%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20the%20planned%20GPI%20could%20be%20a%20game-changer%20against%20hypersonic%20threats%2C%20which%20neither%20country%20currently%20has%20the%20ability%20to%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20US%20weaponry%20has%20defeated%20adjacent%20threats%20like%20Russia's%20Kinzhal%20air-launched%20ballistic%20missile%2C%20current%20missile%20defenses%20would%20likely%20struggle%20against%20actual%20hypersonic%20weapons%20like%20China's%20DF-17%20equipped%20with%20a%20hypersonic%20glide%20vehicle%20or%20Russia's%20Zircon%20scramjet-powered%20hypersonic%20cruise%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECooperation%20on%20the%20GPI%20comes%20as%20the%20US%20and%20Japan%20face%20an%20expanding%20Chinese%20missile%20force%20capable%20of%20targeting%20US%20bases%20in%20Japan%2C%20as%20well%20as%20other%20positions%20in%20the%20Pacific%20region%2C%20and%20increasing%20cooperation%20between%20Moscow%20and%20Beijing%20that%20has%20American%20intelligence%20re-evaluating%20its%20defenses.%20Notably%2C%20Pyongyang%20is%20also%20attempting%20to%20develop%20what%20it%20says%20are%20hypersonic%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrent%20and%20former%20US%20military%20leaders%20have%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20China's%20missiles%2C%20and%20US%20lawmakers%20and%20experts%20have%20said%20that%20the%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-pacific-bases-aircraft-vulnerable-to-chinese-missiles-lawmakers-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elacks%20sufficient%20active%20and%20passive%20defenses%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20defend%20against%20a%20bombardment%20that%20could%20include%20hypersonic%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224523%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Chinese%20soldier%20stands%20at%20attention%20during%20a%20military%20parade%2C%20as%20trucks%20display%20hypersonic%20missiles%20in%20the%20backgorund.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61ba1a94a887ae0018ee825c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDF-17%20medium-range%20ballistic%20missiles%20equipped%20with%20a%20DF-ZF%20hypersonic%20glide%20vehicle%20in%20a%20military%20parade%20to%20mark%20the%2070th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Chinese%20People's%20Republic.%3Cp%3EZoya%20Rusinova%5C%5CTASS%20via%20Getty%20Image%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GPI%20project%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20US%20and%20Japan%20have%20worked%20together%20on%20missile%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20allies%20successfully%20tested%20the%20jointly%20developed%20Standard%20Missile%203%20(SM-3)%20Block%20IIA%20interceptor%20in%20a%20February%202017%20intercept%20of%20a%20ballistic%20missile%20target.%20The%20SM-3%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Aegis%20Ballistic%20Missile%20Defense%20system%2C%20was%20used%20in%20combat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-warships-used-weapon-combat-first-destroy-iranian-missiles-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%20during%20Iran's%20missile%20and%20drone%20strike%20against%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20SM-3%20was%20significant%20not%20only%20because%20of%20its%20unprecedented%20use%20in%20combat%2C%20but%20also%20due%20to%20its%20unique%20capability%20to%20eliminate%20targets%20outside%20of%20the%20Earth's%20atmosphere%2C%20or%20exo-atmospherically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-and-japan-teaming-up-to-defeat-hypersonic-missiles-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715807779000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664523789fc063e829b17ef7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-and-japan-teaming-up-to-defeat-hypersonic-missiles-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20co-development%20comes%20as%20the%20allies%20face%20a%20growing%20Chinese%20missile%20threat%20and%20challenges%20from%20other%20potential%20adversaries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-and-japan-teaming-up-to-defeat-hypersonic-missiles-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20brothers%20allegedly%20stole%20%2425m%20in%2012%20seconds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715807766000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FE575%2Fproduction%2F_133314785_gettyimages-1243263912.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.