2%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f74efcb0ab50d00184ad6ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoe%20Biden%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20debating%20in%202020.%20They've%20agreed%20to%20two%20new%20debates%20in%202024%20%E2%80%94%20ones%20that%20will%20sideline%20decades%20of%20tradition.%3Cp%3EJim%20Watson%2C%20Saul%20Loeb%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Commission%20on%20Presidential%20Debates%20has%20set%20the%20showdowns%20for%2037%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20this%20year%2C%20Biden%20and%20Trump%20are%20doing%20their%20own%20thing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20commission%20told%20BI%20it%20could%20still%20host%20its%20planned%20debates%2C%20but%20Biden%20and%20Trump%20seem%20to%20have%20had%20enough.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20non-partisan%20body%20that's%20set%20the%20locations%2C%20moderators%2C%20and%20formats%20for%20presidential%20debates%20for%20the%20past%2037%20years%20is%20suddenly%20looking%20obsolete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresumptive%20presidential%20candidates%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20went%20around%20the%20Commission%20on%20Presidential%20Debates%20(CPD)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trolls-trump-offers-debates-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20plan%20their%20own%20debate%20schedule%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20on%20June%2027%20with%20what%20will%20be%20the%20earliest%20general%20election%20debate%20in%20US%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20showdown%20in%20Atlanta%20will%20be%20unprecedented%20in%20other%20ways.%20It's%20the%20first%20debate%20in%20decades%20without%20a%20studio%20audience%2C%20and%20appears%20set%20to%20run%20exclusively%20on%20CNN%20platforms%20as%20opposed%20to%20multiple%20major%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CPD%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20was%20established%20to%20ensure%20debates%20%26quot%3Breliably%20take%20place%20and%20reach%20the%20widest%20television%2C%20radio%2C%20and%20streaming%20audience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%202024%20sites%2C%20all%20locations%20of%20higher%20learning%2C%20are%20prepared%20to%20host%20debates%20on%20dates%20chosen%20to%20accommodate%20early%20voters%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20commission%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20execute%20this%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Biden%20and%20Trump%20don't%20seem%20ready%20to%20keep%20the%20tradition%20alive.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20CNN%20debate%20that%20spurned%20the%20commission%2C%20the%20two%20also%20agreed%20to%20a%20September%2010%20debate%20on%20ABC%2C%20and%20the%20Trump%20campaign%20suggested%20two%20additional%20showdowns%20in%20July%20and%20August.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(The%20CPD%20traditionally%20holds%20three%20debates%20beginning%20in%20the%20fall%20%E2%80%94%20not%20four.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reworked%20schedule%20has%20materialized%20as%20both%20sides%20have%20blasted%20the%20CPD.%20The%20RNC%20pulled%20out%20of%20the%20organization%20in%202022%2C%20claiming%20it%20was%20biased%2C%20and%20the%20Biden%20campaign%20confirmed%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F05%2F15%2Fbiden-trump-presidential-debates%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewould%20not%20participate%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20scheduled%20debates%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%2C%20Biden%20campaign%20chair%20Jen%20O'Malley%20Dillon%20criticized%20the%20commission%20for%20%26quot%3Bbuilding%20huge%20spectacles%20with%20large%20audiences%20at%20great%20expense%26quot%3B%20and%20inviting%20%26quot%3Braucous%20or%20disruptive%20partisans%20and%20donors%2C%20who%20consume%20valuable%20debate%20time%20with%20noisy%20spectacles%20of%20approval%20or%20jeering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20surprising%20fall%20from%20grace%20for%20an%20organization%20that%20has%2C%20until%20this%20cycle%2C%20largely%20worked%20without%20complaint%20from%20major%20party%20candidates%20%E2%80%94%20though%20third-party%20candidates%20have%20complained%20that%20the%20commission's%20rules%20box%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20nonprofit%20tax%20information%20filed%20to%20the%20IRS%20in%202022%2C%20the%20CPD%20reported%20having%20over%20%247.6%20million%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-debate-commission-presidential-tradition-over-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715804815000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664511b09fc063e829b16e3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-debate-commission-presidential-tradition-over-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20non-partisan%20body%20that's%20set%20the%20locations%2C%20moderators%2C%20and%20formats%20for%20presidential%20debates%20for%20nearly%2040%20years%20is%20suddenly%20looking%20obsolete.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Geoff%20Weiss)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-debate-commission-presidential-tradition-over-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Spring%20in%20Broadway%E2%80%99s%20Step%3A%20After%20a%20Grim%20Fall%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Theater%20Industry%20Finds%20Reasons%20to%20be%20Upbeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715804761000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FBway-BO-spli.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236005291%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Are%20we%20back%20yet%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20question%20Broadway%20has%20been%20asking%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20as%20the%20theater%20industry%20emerged