3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20in%20a%20chargesheet%20given%20to%20a%20court%20in%20Assam's%20Guwahati%20on%20March%2027%20said%20the%20China-Myanmar%20module%20of%20the%20insurgent%20group%20NSCN(IM)%20gave%20logistics%20and%20other%20support%20to%20the%20proscribed%20terrorist%20organisations%20KYKL%2C%20and%20the%20PLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20has%20seen%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20banned%20Kanglei%20Yaol%20Kanba%20Lup%20(KYKL)%20and%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-dormant-terror-groups-becoming-active-stoking-tension-in-manipur-4379996%5C%22%3EMeitei%20insurgent%20groups%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20National%20Socialist%20Council%20of%20Nagalim%20(Isak-Muivah)%2C%20or%20NSCN(IM)%2C%20is%20a%20Naga%20insurgent%20group%20that%20signed%20a%20framework%20agreement%20with%20the%20government%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20described%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-tweets-about-historic-and-landmake-announcement-1203417%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20step%20to%20bring%20peace%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%2C%20giving%20a%20background%20of%20the%20case%2C%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20said%20the%20Centre%20had%20received%20intelligence%20about%20a%20transnational%20conspiracy%20hatched%20by%20the%20Myanmar-based%20leadership%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bterror%20outfits%26quot%3B%20to%20destabilise%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20Manipur%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bwage%20a%20war%20against%20the%20government%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20KYKL%20and%20PLA%20leadership%20in%20Myanmar%20decided%20to%20infiltrate%20their%20insurgents%20into%20Indian%20territory%20to%20carry%20out%20terror%20attacks%2C%20the%20NIA%20said.%20To%20this%20end%2C%20the%20NSCN(IM)%20leadership%20promised%20safe%20passage%2C%20arms%2C%20ammunition%2C%20expl