egations%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20only%20misleading%20but%20cruel%20and%20vicious%20as%20it%20is%20too%20far%20from%20the%20point%20of%20accuracy%20and%20morally%20not%20ethical%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NSCN(IM)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20tribes%20had%20fought%20with%20the%20Nagas%20in%20the%2090s%20after%20the%20Nagas%20accused%20them%20of%20encroaching%20on%20their%20land.%20Many%20from%20both%20tribes%20were%20killed%20in%20that%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20security%20forces...%20use%20the%20Kukis%20as%20frontal%20forces%20to%20engage%20in%20bloody%20discord%20against%20the%20Nagas%20giving%20all%20logistics%20support%20to%20the%20Kuki%20militant%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20NSCN(IM)%20alleged%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202023%2C%20the%20month%20Meitei-Kuki%20ethnic%20violence%20began%2C%20the%20NSCN(IM)%20had%20asked%20the%20two%20communities%20to%20ensure%20the%20hostilities%20between%20them%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-situation-gets-complicated-as-groups-accuse-each-other-of-attacks-naga-nscn-warns-kukis-4067089%5C%22%3Edo%20not%20affect%20the%20Nagas%3C%2Fa%3E%20living%20in%20the%20violence-hit%20state.%20The%20NSCN(IM)%20had%20alleged%20some%20%26quot%3BKuki%20militants%26quot%3B%20attacked%20a%20village%20where%20members%20of%20the%20Kom%20community%20-%20a%20Naga%20minor%20tribe%20-%20live%20in%20Manipur's%20Kangathei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fq6v4eko_manipur-insurgent-camp-soo_625x300_02_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20assembly%20on%20February%2029%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fend-suspension-of-operations-soo-agreement-with-all-kuki-zo-insurgent-groups-manipur-assembly-in-una