20Gets%20400%20Seats'%3A%20Himanta%20Sarma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20spoke%20of%20a%20fresh%20to-do%20list%20if%20the%20NDA%20gets%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20ongoing%20general%20election.%20Countering%20the%20Opposition%20allegations%20of%20a%20change%20in%20Constitution%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%20today%20that%20the%20focus%20would%20be%20on%20making%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir%20a%20part%20of%20India.%20His%20list%20also%20has%20two%20building%20projects%20--%20temples%20at%20Krishna%20Janambhoomi%20in%20Mathura%20and%20in%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi.%20%26quot%3BYou%20think%20Hindus%20would%20be%20satisfied%20with%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%2C%20speaking%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Jharkhand's%20Ramgarh%2C%20said%20it%20was%20a%20natural%20progression%20of%20the%20party's%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20crossed%20300%20(seats)%20we%20scrapped%20Article%20370%2C%20built%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple.%20Once%20we%20cross%20400%2C%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir%20merges%20with%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20game%20will%20start%20after%20crossing%20400.%20For%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20slogans%20of%20freedom%20are%20being%20raised%20in%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir.%20Crossing%20400%20means%20return%20of%20PoK%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAgitation%20is%20taking%20place%20every%20day%20in%20PoK%20and%20people%20are%20protesting%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20holding%20the%20Indian%20flag%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%20said%20during%20Congress%20rule%2C%20no%20discussion%20was%20held%20in%20Parliament%20regarding%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Congress%20government%20was%20in%20power%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20one%20Kashmir%20is%20in%20India%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Pakistan.%20It%20was%20never%20discussed%20in%20our%20Parliament%20that%20Pakistan%20has%20'Occupied%20Kashmir%2C'%20it%20is%20actually%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20of%20protests%20in%20Pakistan-Occupied%20Kashmir%20was%20highlighted%20by%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20also.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20PoK%20must%20be%20comparing%20their%20situation%20with%20those%20living%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20in%20view%20of%20the%20progress%20there%2C%20he%20had%20said%20yesterday.%20The%20BJP%20has%20ascribed%20the%20high%20turnout%20in%20the%20election%20for%20the%20Srinagar%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20to%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%2014%20per%20cent%20polling%20in%202019%2C%20the%20figure%20this%20time%20rose%20to%2038%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20highest%20since%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715795220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F4ro1jrk_himanta-sarma-pok_625x300_15_May_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-pak-occupied-kashmir-to-be-part-of-india-himanta-sarma-on-400-paar-goal-5671774%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20spoke%20of%20a%20fresh%20to-do%20list%20if%20the%20NDA%20gets%20400%20seats%20in%20the%20ongoing%20general%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-pak-occupied-kashmir-to-be-part-of-india-himanta-sarma-on-400-paar-goal-5671774%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-pak-occupied-kashmir-to-be-part-of-india-himanta-sarma-on-400-paar-goal-5671774%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-pak-occupi