r%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22pt%5C%22%3EHomens%20armados%20resgatam%20chefe%20de%20gangue%20na%20Fran%C3%A7a%20e%20matam%202%20agentes%20penitenci%C3%A1rios%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMohamed%20Amra%2C%20apelidado%20de%20''The%20Fly''%2C%20era%20sentenciado%20a%20pris%C3%A3o%20perp%C3%A9tua.%20A%20escolta%20dele%20foi%20emboscada%20pr%C3%B3ximo%20de%20um%20ped%C3%A1gio%20em%20Incarville.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2%20agentes%20morreram%2C%201%20segue%20gravemente%20ferido.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FdZ5ksBUR2r%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FdZ5ksBUR2r%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Submundo%20Criminal%20(%40submundodocrime)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsubmundodocrime%2Fstatus%2F1790407672547709073%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCTV%20images%20from%20the%20scene%20viewed%20by%20AFP%20show%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20assault%20on%20the%20prison%20van%2C%20although%20a%20passing%20truck%20obscures%20some%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20assailants%20can%20be%20seen%20arriving%20from%20behind%20the%20convoy%2C%20with%20prosecutors%20saying%20they%20jumped%20out%20of%20a%20white%20Audi%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prisoner%2C%20Mohamed%20Amra%2C%20was%20being%20escorted%20that%20day%20by%20five%20guards%20--%20a%20%26quot%3Blevel%20three%26quot%3B%20protection%20that%20is%20the%20second-highest%20available%20for%20inmate%20transport%20in%20France%2C%20reserved%20for%20those%20implicated%20in%20terror%20or%20organised%20crime%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuards%20were%20%26quot%3Bof%20course%20armed%26quot%3B%2C%20Beccuau%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Binitial%20findings%20from%20the%20scene%20lead%20us%20to%20think%20that%20some%20may%20have%20used%20their%20service%20weapons%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20team%20had%20on%20them%20only%20%26quot%3Ba%20basic%20Sig%20Sauer%20(automatic%20pistol)%20against%20military%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Frederic%20Liakhoff%2C%20a%20representative%20for%20the%20FO%20union%20at%20the%20prison%20in%20the%20northern%20city%20of%20Caen%20where%20Amra%20was%20being%20transported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Very%2C%20very%20loud'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20their%20%26quot%3Blong%20weapons%26quot%3B%20(rifles)%2C%20the%20attackers%20%26quot%3Bfired%20multiple%20times%20on%20the%20two%20prison%20service%20vehicles%2C%20killing%20two%20agents%20and%20wounding%20three%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Beccuau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20first%20time%20a%20French%20prison%20guard%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20line%20of%20duty%20since%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20the%20life%20of%20one%20of%20the%20three%20men%20injured%20remains%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20%26quot%3Bloud%20gunshots%2C%20very%2C%20very%20loud%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jerome%20Barbier%2C%20who%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20tend%20his%20beehives%20near%20the%20Incarville%20toll%20station%20when%20the%20attack%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%2C%20there%20was%20a%20pause%20for%20one%20or%20two%20minutes%2C%20a%20big%20blast%2C%20two%20gunshots%20and%20then%20it%20was%20all%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20local%20resident%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20minute%20and%2040%20seconds%20into%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20surveillance%20video%20shows%20a%20man%20--%20apparently%20a%20guard%20--%20being%20forced%20towards%20the%20prison%20van%20at%20gunpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstants%20later%2C%20a%20man%20wearing%20white%20trainers%20climbs%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20and%20five%20black-clad%20accomplices%20flee%20before%20an%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20Tuesday%2C%20%26quot%3Btwo%20vehicles%20were%20found%20burned%20out%26quot%3B%20not%20far%20from%20the%20scene%2C%20Beccuau%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20crime%20scene%20reveals%20the%20extreme%20violence%20the%20criminals%20we%20are%20hunting%20for%20perpetrated%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%20after%20visiting%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20resolve%20of%20judges%20and%20investigators%20will%20rise%20to%20the%20challenge%20of%20this%20violence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterior%20Minister%20Gerald%20Darmanin%20told%20broadcaster%20RTL%20that%20%26quot%3Bconsiderable%26quot%3B%20resources%20had%20been%20deployed%20to%20find%20escapee%20Amra%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bgang%20who%20freed%20him%20in%20deplorable%20circumstances%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20450%20police%20and%20gendarmes%26quot%3B%20were%20in%20the%20field%20Tuesday%20in%20the%20Eure%20department%20where%20the%20attack%20took%20place%2C%20he%20added%2C%20saying%20France%20had%20also%20called%20in%20%26quot%3Binternational%20cooperation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715788080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvrij788g_france-police-van_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-prison-van-attack-mohamed-amra-the-fly-two-minutes-of-extreme-violence-in-french-prison-van-escape-5671182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20attack%20on%20a%20prison%20van%20in%20northern%20France%20that%20left%20two%20guards%20dead%20and%20three%20wounded%20began%20at%2010%3A57%20am%20(0857%20GMT)%20and%20lasted%20just%20two%20minutes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-prison-van-attack-mohamed-amra-the-fly-two-minutes-of-extreme-violence-in-french-prison-van-escape-5671182%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffrance-prison-van-attack-mohamed-amra-the-fly-two-minutes-of-extreme-violence-in-french-prison-van-escape-5671182%2Famp%