-since-women-started-saeed-anwars-sexist-rant-slammed-on-social-media-5670953%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdivorces-have-shot-up-since-women-started-saeed-anwars-sexist-rant-slammed-on-social-media-5670953%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Woman%20Used%20AI%20Therapy%20After%20A%20Panic%20Attack.%20Read%20Her%20Experience%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20we%20are%20living%20in%20the%20era%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence.%20The%20possibilities%20of%20AI%20are%20limitless%2C%20and%20it%20is%20only%20just%20beginning%20to%20be%20explored.%C2%A0Now%2C%20millions%20of%20people%20are%20turning%20to%20AI%20for%20one%20of%20the%20most%20personal%20tasks%3A%20therapy.%20With%20a%20global%20shortage%20of%20therapists%20and%20a%20surge%20in%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20these%20AI-powered%20bots%20offer%20cheap%2C%C2%A0convenient%2C%20and%20immediate%20support.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20UK%20revealed%20that%20she%20turned%20to%20an%20AI%20therapist%20when%20she%20had%20a%20panic%20attack%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F05%2F15%2Fturned-ai-therapist-a-panic-attack-20769361%2F%5C%22%3EMetro%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20Recounting%20her%20experience%2C%20Molly%20Pennington%20said%20that%20she%20was%20''outright%20cynical''%20about%20using%20it%2C%20but%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20chance.%20She%20first%20typed%C2%A0AI%20Therapy%C2%A0into%20Google%20and%20clicked%20on%20the%20first%20link%20that%20greeted%20her%20with%20a%C2%A0disclaimer%3A%20''This%20is%20not%20a%20replacement%20for%20medical%20or%20professional%20help''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20then%20connected%20with%20an%20AI%20therapist%20who%20asked%20for%20her%20name%20and%20how%20it%20could%20help%20her%20through%20automated%20messages.%20Ms%20Pennington%20explained%20that%20she%C2%A0was%20having%20a%20panic%20attack.%20The%20bot%20then%C2%A0guided%20her%20through%20several%20grounding%20exercises%20focused%20on%20her%20breathing.%20The%20woman%20claimed%20the%20exercises%20helped%20her%20and%20her%20panic%20attacks%20started%20to%20ease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20she%20had%20a%20positive%20experience%2C%20she%20couldn't%20get%20over%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20wasn't%20communicating%20with%20a%20human%20and%20felt%20a%20little%20uneasy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Pennington%20told%20%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20''Somehow%20it%20felt%20performative%20and%20disingenuous.%20I've%20never%20had%20that%20feeling%20in%20traditional%20therapy%20%E2%80%93%20though%20admittedly%20this%20could%20be%20because%20I've%20been%20lucky%20to%20only%20work%20with%20fantastic%20therapists%20and%20because%20I%20knew%20they%20were%20human!''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20also%20concerned%20whether%20an%C2%A0AI%20therapist%20would%20be%20able%20to%20handle%20a%20more%20complicated%C2%A0%20situation%20than%20a%20panic%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Don't%20misunderstand%2C%20I'm%20glad%20I%20tried%20it%20and%20it%20certainly%20helped%20me%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20but%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'm%20not%20sure%20if%20I%20would%20personally%20use%20AI%20therapy%20again%2C''%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20can't%20see%20myself%20reaching%20for%20it%20for%20general%20advice%2C%20like%20if%20I'm%20anxious%20about%20work%20or%20have%20an%20argument%20with%20a%20family%20member.%20And%20if%20I%20was%20having%20a%20panic%20attack%2C%20I%20think%20I%20would%20prefer%20to%20watch%20a%20YouTube%20video%20of%20a%20guided%20grounding%20activity%2C''%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20also%20noted%20that%20private%20therapy%20is%20expensive%20and%20not%20everybody%20can%20afford%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Only%20time%20will%20tell%20if%20AI%20therapy%20is%20better%20than%20nothing.%20I%20just%20hope%20our%20most%20vulnerable%20don't%20pay%20the%20price%20while%20we%20wait%20for%20an%20answer%2C''%20she%20said%20further.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715785920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fi99jbqt_molly-pennington_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-had-a-panic-attack-so-she-turned-to-an-ai-therapist-for-help-read-her-experience-5670636%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20in%20the%20UK%20revealed%20that%20she%20turned%20to%20an%20AI%20therapist%20for%20mental%20health%20support%20when%20she%20had%20a%20panic%20attack.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-had-a-panic-attack-so-she-turned-to-an-ai-therapist-for-help-read-her-experience-5670636%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-had-a-panic-attack-so-she-turned-to-an-ai-therapist-for-help-read-her-experience-5670636%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fuk-woman-had-a-panic-attack-so-she-turned-to-an-ai-therapist-for-help-read-her-experience-5670636%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20urges%20NBFCs%20to%20maintain%20constant%20vigil%20against%20potential%20risks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715785729000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F21%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1713715550-9425.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fnews%2Frbi-urges-nbfcs-to-maintain-constant-vigil-against-potential-risks-124051501379_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Swaminathan%20said%20that%20NBFCs%20are%20highly%20exposed%20to%20a%20slew%20of%20risks%20which%20can%20affect%20their%20financial%20and%20operational%20status%20like%20cybersecurity%20and%20other%20risks%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.c