0pose%20a%20risk.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it%20has%20been%20observed%20that%20irregularly%20sized%20advertising%20boards%20have%20been%20installed%20around%20the%20roads%2Fprivate%20constructions%20within%20the%20boundary%20of%20the%20railway%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20civic%20body's%20notice%2C%20sent%20today%20to%20the%20Central%20and%20Western%20Railways%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20light%20of%20this%2C%20as%20an%20additional%20measure%20to%20prevent%20accidents%2C%20the%20Additional%20Municipal%20Commissioner%20(City)%20has%20directed%20the%20immediate%20removal%20of%20all%20advertising%20boards%20larger%20than%2040x40%20feet%20within%20the%20boundary%20of%20the%20railway%20administration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notice%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ghatkopar%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20rescue%20work%20is%20continuing%2C%20as%20many%20families%20remain%20at%20spot%20in%20search%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hoarding%20had%20collapsed%20during%20a%20spell%20of%20bad%20weather%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20with%20a%20petrol%20pump%20buried%20under%20it%2C%20the%20rescue%20work%20has%20been%20moving%20slowly.%20Sources%20said%20since%20the%20accident%2C%20petrol%20has%20been%20leaking%20from%20some%20of%20the%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20size%20and%20weight%20of%20the%20hoarding%2C%20rescue%20workers%20fear%20they%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20reach%20the%20trapped%20people%20in%20time.%20Even%20though%20only%20upto%2040x40%20feet%20hoardings%20are%20allowed%20by%20the%20civic%20body%2C%20this%20one%20was%20120x120%20feet%20and%20weighed%20250%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuestions%20are%20being%20raised%20over%20who%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20accident%20%E2%80%93%20the%20civic%20body%2C%20the%20railways%20or%20or%20Bhavesh%20Bhinde%2C%20owner%20of%20the%20Igo%20Media%20Company%2C%20which%20put%20up%20the%20hoarding%2C%20ignoring%20all%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIgo%20Media%20has%20erected%20four%20illegal%20hoardings%20on%20GRP%20land%20in%20Ghatkopar.%20Now%2C%20while%20the%20BMC%20is%20busy%20removing%20the%20remaining%20three%20hoardings%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20is%20searching%20for%20Bhavesh%20Bhinde.%20A%20case%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715784780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2vtca6io_mumbai-hoarding-collapse_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-mumbais-billboard-tragedy-civic-body-wants-large-hoardings-out-5670610%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Irregularly%20shaped%20hoardings%2C%20especially%20those%20larger%20than%2040x40%20feet%20will%20be%20removed%20immediately%20from%20the%20boundary%20of%20the%20railway%20administration%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20civic%20body%20said%20a%20day%20after%20a%20250-tonne%20hoarding%20fell%2C%20killing%2014%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-mumbais-billboard-tragedy-civic-body-wants-large-hoardings-out-5670610%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-mumbais-billboard-tragedy-civic-body-wants-large-hoardings-out-5670610%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-mumbais-billboard-tragedy-civic-body-wants-large-hoardings-out-5670610%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22L%26amp%3BT%20Finance%20aims%20at%2025%25%20CAGR%20over%20next%20few%20years%2C%20retail%20lending%20in%20focus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715784684000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F03%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1712114417-8392.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies