r%20as%20he%20is%20in%20No.%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20leader's%20role%20is%20to%20identify%20the%20best%20potential%20and%20show%20it%20to%20the%20world.%20If%20there%20is%20one%20regret%20I%20have%20in%20my%20seven%20years%20of%20captaincy%20is%20that%20me%20and%20as%20a%20team%20never%20managed%20to%20use%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20to%20the%20best%20of%20his%20potential.%20And%20the%20reason%20was%20down%20to%20combinations.%20You%20can%20only%20play%20one%20player%20at%20No.%203.%20And%20as%20a%20leader%2C%20you%20have%20to%20think%20about%20the%20other%2010%20players%20in%20the%20XI%20as%20well.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20way%20more%20effective%20at%20No.%203%2C%20but%20was%20equally%20good%20at%20No.%207%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gambhir%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMtzm6qJKgVk%5C%22%3ESportskeeda%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20also%20a%20team%20man.%20Anyone%20can%20be%20a%20good%20player%2C%20but%20being%20a%20team%20man%20is%20a%20difficult%20task.%20Whether%20you%20play%20him%20at%20No.%206%20or%207%20or%20bench%20him%2C%20he%20was%20always%20smiling%20and%20always%20ready%20to%20perform%20for%20the%20team.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20appointed%20him%20as%20the%20vice-captain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715781660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F1mbg65ro_aa_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-reveals-regret-as-kolkata-knight-riders-captain-says-never-managed-to-use-5653846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20batter%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20was%20the%20most%20successful%20captain%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-reveals-regret-as-kolkata-knight-riders-capt