%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%20over%20Rs%2035%20crore%20in%20cash%20from%20a%20flat%20linked%20to%20his%20personal%20secretary%20and%20the%20latter's%20house%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Alam%20was%20questioned%20for%20over%20nine%20hours%20at%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20office%20in%20Ranchi%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20he%20was%20called%20again%20on%20Wednesday.%20He%20was%20interrogated%20for%20six%20hours%20and%20was%20arrested%20for%20not%20cooperating%20with%20the%20investigation%2C%20ED%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20had%20raided%20a%202BHK%20flat%20in%20Ranchi%20occupied%20by%20Jehangir%20Alam%2C%20a%20house%20help%20of%20the%20minister's%20Personal%20Secretary%20Sanjiv%20Lal%2C%20last%20week%20and%20recovered%20Rs%2035.23%20crore%20from%20there%20and%20an%20additional%20over%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20from%20other%20premises.%20A%20total%20of%20Rs%2037%20crore%20was%20seized.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lal%20and%20Jehangir%20Alam%20were%20arrested%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20the%20next%20day%20and%20are%20currently%20in%20ED's%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20against%20Mr%20Alam%20and%20his%20aide%20is%20related%20to%20the%20alleged%20Jharkhand%20tender%20scam%2C%20under%20which%20commissions%20were%20collected%20and%20then%20distributed%20under%20Mr%20Lal's%20supervision.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2070-year-old%20Congress%20leader%20was%20first%20elected%20to%20the%20Jharkhand%20Assembly%20in%202000%20and%20has%20also%20served%20as%20its%20Speaker.%20His%20arrest%20comes%20months%20after%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20and%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20leader%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20the%20land%20scam%20case.%20Mr%20Soren%20had%20resigned%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20just%20before%20he%20was%20officially%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715781060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fqesp06p8_alamgir-alam_625x300_06_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-minister-alamgir-alam-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-5670087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jharkhand%20Rural%20Development%20Minister%20Alamgir%20Alam%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20seizure%20of%20over%20Rs%2030%20crore%20in%20cash%20from%20a%20flat%20linked%20to%20his%20personal%20secretary%20and%20the%20latter's%20house%20help.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-minister-alamgir-alam-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-5670087%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-minister-alamgir-alam-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-5670087%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-minister-alamgir-alam-arrested-by-enforcement-directorate-in-money-laundering-case-5670087%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Indians%20Are%20Still%20Stuck%20On%20Ship%20Months%20After%20It%20Hit%20US%20Bridge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20morning%20of%20March%2026%2C%20a%20container%20ship%20hit%20a%20major%20commuter%20bridge%20in%20Baltimore%2C%20collapsing%20it%20within%20seconds%2C%20killing%20six%20and%20halting%20shipping%20traffic%20at%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20ports%20on%20the%20US%20East%20Coast.%20The%20Singapore-flagged%20container%20ship%20Dali%20and%20the%20crew%20-%2020%20Indian%20and%20one%20Sri%20Lankan%20-%20have%20remained%20in%20place%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202.6-km-long%2C%20four-lane%20Francis%20Scott%20Key%20Bridge%20over%20the%20Patapsco%20River%20came%20crashing%20down%20after%20being%20struck%20by%20the%20984-foot%20ship.%20Several%20video%20footage%20showed%20nearly%20all%20the%20ship's%20lights%20going%20off%20shortly%20before%20the%20stunning%20collapse.%20Now%2C%20a%20preliminary%20report%20by%20federal%20investigators%20released%20Tuesday%20said%20the%20Dali%20suffered%20two%20electricity%20blackouts%20in%20the%20moments%20before%20the%20disaster.%20The%20report%20by%20the%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20(NTSB)%20also%20detailed%20two%20blackouts%20about%20ten%20hours%20before%20leaving%20Baltimore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20crews%20demolished%20part%20of%20the%20bridge%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20free%20the%20Dali.%20Authorities%20hope%20that%20it%20would%20help%20the%20crew%20move%20a%20bit%20closer%20to%20a%20reunion%20with%20their%20families%2C%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20deboard%20the%20ship%20due%20to%20visa%20restrictions%20and%20investigations%20by%20the%20NTSB%20and%20FBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJim%20Lawrence%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Dali%20owner%20Grace%20Ocean%20Private%20Ltd.%2C%20recently%20told%20IANS%20that%20the%20Indian%20crew%20members%20are%20on%20board%20and%20%26quot%3Bin%20good%20spirits%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20addition%20to%20performing%20normal%20duties%20on%20board%20the%20ship%2C%20they%20are%20also%20assisting%20with%20the%20investigations%20and%20with%20the%20ongoing%20salvage%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Lawrence%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20FBI%20launched%20a%20criminal%20probe%20targeting%20the%20ship%2C%20with%20its%20agents%20boarding%20the%20Dali%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation.%20The%20crew%20has%20been%20left%20almost%20without%20communication%20with%20the%20outside%20world%20as%20their%20cellphones%20have%20been%20seized%20by%20the%20FBI%20as%20part%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Baltimore%20International%20Seafarers'%20Centre%20The%20Rev.%20Joshua%20Messick%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20has%20been%20given%20SIM%20cards%20and%20temporary%20cell%20phones%20without%20data%20included%2C%20Mr%20Messick%20told%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20received%20care%20packages%20-%20including%20Indian%20snacks%20and%20quits%20-%20from%20various%20community%20groups%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-69011124%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20BBC%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NTSB%20said%20the%20Dali%20was%20just%200.6%20miles%20from%20the%20bridge%20when%20the%20electrical%20breakers%20that%20fed%20most%20of%20the%20ship's%20equipment%20and%20lighting%20unexpectedly%20tripped%2C%20causing%20the%20first%20blackout.%20It%20lost%20propulsion%20and%20steering%20and%20began%20to%20drift%20off%20course.%20The%20crew%20managed%20to%20restore%20power%20briefly%2C%20but%20with%20the%20Dali%20just%200.2%20miles%20from%20the%20bridge%2C%20the%20lights%20went%20out%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20promised%20last%20month%20to%20%26quot%3Bmove%20heaven%20and%20earth%26quot%3B%20to%20rebuild%20the%20bridge%2C%20pledging%20federal%20funds%20and%20saying%20a%20new%20channel%20for%20shipping%20traffic%20would%20open%20by%20the%20end%20of%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715780400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fd7kce0t8_baltimore-bridge-collapse-reuters_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-indians-are-still-stuck-on-ship-months-after-it-hit-us-bridge-5670373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20early%20morning%20of%20March%2026%2C%20a%20container%20ship%20hit%20a%20major%20commuter%20bridge%20in%20Baltimore%2C%20collapsing%20it%20within%20seconds%2C%20killing%20six%20and%20halting%20shipping%20traffic%20at%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20ports%20on%20the%20US%20East%20Coast.