ss%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Farming%20was%20never%20my%20plan%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20Harshit%20says%20that%20farming%20was%20not%20even%20%E2%80%9Cremotely%20on%20his%20plans%20for%20the%20future%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20he%20was%20interested%20in%20marketing%20and%20after%20his%20schooling%2C%20he%20went%20to%20the%20UK%20to%20study%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20from%20my%20family%20is%20in%20farming%20and%20neither%20did%20I%20ever%20think%20that%20I%20would%20end%20up%20in%20the%20agriculture%20sector.%20In%202017%2C%20I%20was%20pursuing%20a%20BBA%20degree%20and%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20career%20in%20marketing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20was%20very%20interested%20in%20health%20and%20fitness%20and%20that%20is%20what%20led%20him%20to%20pursue%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAvocados%20were%20very%20easily%20available%20to%20us%20and%20high%20in%20nutrition.%20I%20used%20to%20love%20eating%20them%20and%20consumed%20them%20almost%20every%20day%20in%20the%20UK.%20One%20day%2C%20I%20just%20flipped%20the%20box%20and%20saw%20the%20packing%20which%20said%20it%20was%20made%20in%20Israel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaken%20aback%2C%20he%20started%20researching%20more%20on%20how%20a%20dry%20and%20hot%20country%20like%20Israel%20can%20grow%20avocados.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsh%20started%20with%20a%20few%20plants%20and%20now%20has%20a%2010%20acre%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350002%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsh%20started%20with%20a%20few%20plants%20and%20now%20has%20a%2010-acre%20farm.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20soil%20and%20temperature%20it%20needed%20to%20grow.%20It%20needs%20a%20temperature%20below%2030%20degrees%20and%20acidic%20soil%20with%20good%20drainage.%20I%20was%20very%20intrigued%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20how%20Israel%20did%20it%20with%20such%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F139546%2Ftemperatures-water-atms-bengaluru%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh%20temperatures%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUpon%20research%2C%20I%20found%20out%20that%20Israel%20has%20successfully%20grown%20various%20varieties%20under%20controlled%20conditions%20and%20has%20even%20made%20new%20hybrid%20varieties.%20The%20country%20has%20been%20exporting%20the%20fruit%20for%20decades%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20market%20enthusiast%2C%20Harhsit%20realised%20that%20the%20trend%20of%20eating%20the%20fruit%20would%20soon%20catch%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20huge%20demand%20for%20the%20fruit%20in%20the%20west%20which%20means%20that%20it%20will%20reach%20India%20soon.%20This%20gave%20me%20an%20idea%20and%20an%20opportunity%20to%20capitalise%20on%20it.%20I%20thought