C%20the%20methods%20used%20in%20South%20India%20differ%20from%20those%20used%20in%20Central%20India%20where%20I%20am%20based.%20Expecting%20similar%20results%20from%20cheaper%20plants%20without%20considering%20these%20factors%20may%20lead%20to%20disappointment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Harshit%20Godha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715777750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Urban%20farmer%20Harshit%20Godha%20took%20inspiration%20from%20Israeli%20farmers%20growing%20avocadoes%20and%20has%20successfully%20grown%20the%20fruit%20in%20India.%20He%20shares%20how%20you%20can%20grow%20them%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350000%2Fhow-to-grow-avocado-in-india-urban-farmer-harshit-godha-imports-saplings-from-israel-teaches-farming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rising%20Sea%20Levels%20May%20Force%20This%20Country%20To%20Move%20Its%20Capital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThailand%20may%20have%20to%20consider%20relocating%20its%20capital%20Bangkok%20because%20of%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20country's%20climate%20change%20office%20told%20AFP%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProjections%20consistently%20show%20that%20low-lying%20Bangkok%20risks%20being%20inundated%20by%20the%20ocean%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20the%20bustling%20capital%20already%20battles%20flooding%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavich%20Kesavawong%2C%20deputy%20director-general%20of%20the%20government's%20department%20of%20climate%20change%20and%20environment%2C%20warned%20that%20the%20city%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20adapt%20with%20the%20world%20on%20its%20current%20warming%20pathway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20are%20beyond%20the%201.5%20(degrees%20Celsius)%20already%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20increase%20in%20global%20temperatures%20from%20pre-industrial%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we%20have%20to%20come%20back%20and%20think%20about%20adaptation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20imagine%20Bangkok%20will%20be%20under%20water%20already%2C%20if%20we%20stay%20in%20our%20(current)%20circumstance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangkok's%20city%20government%20is%20exploring%20measures%20that%20include%20building%20dikes%2C%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20those%20used%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20%26quot%3Bwe've%20been%20thinking%20about%20moving%26quot%3B%2C%20Pavich%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20discussions%20were%20still%20hypothetical%20and%20the%20issue%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20complex%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersonally%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20good%20choice%2C%20so%20we%20can%20separate%20the%20capital%2C%20the%20government%20areas%2C%20and%20business%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBangkok%20(would)%20still%20be%20the%20government%20capital%2C%20but%20move%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EClimate%20impacts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20move%20is%20still%20a%20long%20way%20from%20being%20adopted%20as%20policy%2C%20it%20would%20not%20be%20unprecedented%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndonesia%20will%20inaugurate%20this%20year%20its%20new%20capital%20Nusantara%2C%20which%20will%20replace%20sinking%20and%20polluted%20Jakarta%20as%20the%20country's%20political%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mammoth%20move%20has%20been%20controversial%20and%20extremely%20expensive%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20price%20tag%20of%20%2432%20billion-%2435%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThailand%20is%20suffering%20the%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20across%20a%20range%20of%20sectors%2C%20from%20farmers%20struggling%20with%20heat%20and%20drought%20to%20tourism%20businesses%20affected%20by%20coral%20bleaching%20and%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20closed%20several%20national%20parks%20in%20response%20to%20recent%20coral%20bleaching%20and%20Pavich%20said%20further%20closures%20were%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20save%20our%20nature%2C%20so%20we%20think%20that%20we%20will%20do%20any%20measure%20to%20protect%20our%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Pavich%20acknowledged%20that%20government%20efforts%20to%20tackle%20the%20growing%20problem%20of%20air%20pollution%2C%20particularly%20in%20Thailand's%20north%2C%20had%20yet%20to%20bear%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegislation%20focused%20on%20clean%20air%20passed%20this%20year%20and%20Pavich%20said%20national%20parks%20officials%20had%20stepped%20up%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20and%20put%20out%20fires%20in%20protected%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agriculture%20sector%20is%20very%20challenging%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20continued%20post-harvest%20burning%20that%20is%20a%20major%20contributor%20to%20seasonal%20haze.%20An%20improvement%20is%20not%20likely%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20immediately%2C%20his%20department%20--%20part%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Natural%20Resources%20and%20Environment%20--%20is%20pushing%20Thailand's%20first%20climate%20change%20legislation%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20works%20since%20at%20least%202019%20but%20was%20shelved%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavich%20said%20the%20legislation%2C%20which%20includes%20provisions%20on%20everything%20from%20carbon%20pricing%20to%20mitigation%20and%20adaptation%20measures%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20pass%20into%20law%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThailand%20is%20targeting%20carbon%20neutrality%20by%202050%2C%20and%20net-zero%20by%202065.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715777460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fojpk0nt8_bangkok-the-capital-of-thailand_625x300_23_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frising-sea-levels-may-force-this-country-to-move-its-capital-thailand-bangkok-5669957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thailand%20may%20have%20to%20consider%20relocating%20its%20capital%20Bangkok%20because%20of%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20country's%20climate%20change%20office%20told%20AFP%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frising-sea-levels-may-force-this-country-to-move-its-capital-thailand-bangkok-5669957%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frising-sea-levels-may-force-this-country-to-move-its-capital-thailand-bangkok-5669957%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frising-sea-levels-may-force-this-country-to-move-its-capital-thailand-bangkok-5669957%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%202%20Cr%20Salary%20to%202%20Million%20Followers%3A%20How%20%E2%80%98FoodPharmer%E2%80%99%20Started%20A%20Food%20Revolution%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20grab%20a%20food%20item%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20our%20instinct%20is%20often%20to%20check%20the%20expiry%20date.%20But%20do%20we%20also%20spare%20just%20a%20couple%20more%20minutes%20to%20scan%20the%20ingredient%20list%3F%20These%20extra%20moments%20could%20be%20crucial%2C%20shaping%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20food%20we%E2%80%99re%20putting%20into%20our%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPackaged%20food%20has%20become%20integral%20to%20our%20lives%2C%20whether%20we%20like%20it%20or%20not.%20Therefore%2C%20making%20conscious%20decisions%20to%20opt%20for%20packaged%20foods%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20pose%20additional%20risks%20is%20essential.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20step%2C%20but%20it%20can%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20our%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20reports%20have%20emphasised%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20carefully%20reading%20food%20labels.%20The%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20released%20dietary%20guidelines%20for%20Indians%20on%20May%208%2C%20cautioning%20that%20the%20information%20provided%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348030%2Fmdh-everest-sambhar-masala-fssai-guidelines-food-safety-ethylene-oxide-fish-curry-masala-singapore-hong-kong%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epackaged%20food%20labels%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20often%20be%20misleading.%20%E2%80%9CHealth%20claims%20on%20packaged%20food%20are%20designed%20to%20catch%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20attention%20and%20convince%20them%20that%20the%20product%20is%20healthy.%20Always%20read%20food%20label%20information%20to%20know%20about%20the%20contents%20inside%20the%20pack%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20guidelines%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20fooled%20by%20labels%20like%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98no%20sugar%20added%E2%80%99.%20One%20man%20who%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20decode%20these%20food%20labels%20and%20teach%20Indians%20how%20to%20read%20them%20is%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20aka%20%E2%80%98foodpharmer%E2%80%99%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20year%2C%20this%2032-year-old%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20charge%20in%20promoting%20health%20literacy%20and%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%20before%20making%20purchases.%20Through%20his%20Instagram%20page%2C%20he%20has%20gathered%20a%20following%20of%20over%202.2%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20left%20behind%20a%20lucrative%20Rs%202%20crore%20job%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20this%20certified%20health%20coach%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20spark%20a%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20revolution%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndians%20are%20educated%20but%20not%20health%20literate.%20I%E2%80%99m%20therefore%20focusing%20on%20health%20literacy%2C%20with%20my%20major%20target%20being%20children.%20You%20should%20develop%20healthy%20habits%20in%20children%20from%20day%20one%20and%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20junk%20to%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20developing%20health%20issues%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHolding%20large%20FMCG%20conglomerates%20accountable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%2090s%20Kolkata%2C%20Revant%20had%20a%20regular%20childhood%2C%20which%20included%20biscuits%2C%20packaged%20foods%2C%20and%20drinks%20like%20Bournvita.%20The%20young%20boy%20was%20then%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20the%20food%20he%20consumed%2C%20like%20millions%20of%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Revant%20wants%20Indians%20to%20learn%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Frevantt-1715774320-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0