ssing%20with%20her%20sister%2C%20who%20is%20a%20designer%2C%20Nupur%20zeroed%20in%20on%20making%20craft%20items%20out%20of%20pine%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20small%20step%20towards%20a%20big%20issue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20launching%20their%20startup%20%E2%80%98Pirul%20Handicrafts%E2%80%99%2C%20Nupur%20and%20Sharvari%20mobilised%20the%20villagers%20to%20collect%20pine%20waste%20from%20nearby%20forests.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20collecting%20these%20pine%20needles%2C%20we%20clean%20and%20soak%20them%20in%20water%20for%20some%20time.%20Thereafter%2C%20we%20make%20simple%20products%20like%20tea%20coasters%20using%20the%20coiling%20technique.%20Historically%2C%20coiled%20baskets%20made%20from%20this%20technique%20are%20either%20hay%20or%20grass-based%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1715763820.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nupur%20(left)%2C%20along%20with%20her%20sister%20Sharvari%2C%20started%20%E2%80%98PIRUL%20Handicrafts%E2%80%99%20to%20make%20artefacts%20from%20pine%20needles.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1715763820.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1715763820-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1715763820-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1715763820-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1715763820-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350008%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENupur%20(left)%20and%20her%20sister%20Sharvari%20started%20%E2%80%98PIRUL%20Handicrafts%E2%80%99%20to%20make%20artefacts%20from%20pine%20needles.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20team%20manufactures%20various%20handicraft%20products%20like%20tea%20coasters%2C%20earrings%2C%20storage%20boxes%2C%20handbags%2C%20serving%20trays%2C%20table%20mats%2C%20and%20planters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%2015%20women%20initially%2C%20the%20team%20has%20expanded%20to%20100%20women%20from%20seven%20villages%20like%20KhetiKhan%2C%20Tyarsun%2C%20Patan%2C%20Chaanmari%2C%20Panda%2C%20Paati%2C%20and%20Jhulaghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunita%20Moni%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20with%20the%20startup%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20used%20to%20rear%20livestock%20and%20grow%20wheat%20and%20paddy%20on%20two%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20our%20land.%20Often%2C%20we%20would%20incur%20huge%20losses%20because%20of%20forest%20fires%20that%20would%20burn%20down%20our%20crops%2C%20fodder%20for%20our%20cows%2C%20even%20houses%2C%20and%20dry%20water%20resources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20pine%20waste%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20beautiful%20craft%20items.%20It%20is%20exciting%20to%20make%20new%20designs%20every%20day.%20With%20this%2C%20my%20monthly%20income%20has%20also%20increased%20from%20Rs%201%2C500%20to%20Rs%205%2C000.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20enrol%20both%20of%20my%20kids%20in%20private%20schools.%20Over%20these%20years%2C%20I%20also%20saved%20some%20of%20this%20amount%20to%20buy%20one%20%3Cem%3Etola%20%3C%2Fem%3E(nearly%2012%20grams)%20of%20gold%20to%20secure%20the%20future%20of%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Collectively%2C%20these%20women%20diverted%2020%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20to%20something%20useful.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPirul-1-1715763906-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350010%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECollectively%2C%20these%20women%20diverted%2020%2C000%20kg%20of%20waste%20to%20something%20useful.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20these%20rural%20women%20have%20sold%20about%2012%2C000%20products%20and%20have%20established%20a%20large%20customer%20base%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Hyderabad%20cities%20in%20India%2C%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20social%20angle%20is%20one%20of%20the%20contributing%20factors%2C%20our%20products%20have%20also%20become%20popular%20for%20their%20durability%20and%20better%20finish%20compared%20to%20other%20eco-friendly%20products%20like%20bamboo.%20While%20bamboo%20products%20are%20prone%20to%20fungal%20attack%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20worry%20in%20pine%20needle%20products%20as%20they%20are%20naturally-resistant%20to%20fungus%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20startup%2C%20Nupur%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20able%20to%20contribute%20towards%20society%20in%20a%20positive%20way.%20Interestingly%2C%20we%20have%20not%20observed%20any%2