grees.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%E2%80%99ve%20zeroed%20in%20on%20your%20interests%2C%20do%20a%20bachelors%20in%20science%2Fengineering%2C%20masters%20and%20a%20PhD%20to%20equip%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDevelop%20technical%2Fhands%20on%20skills.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20how%20important%20AI%20and%20Machine%20learning%20(ML)%20has%20become%20today%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20develop%20these%20skills%2C%20states%20Akshata.%20%E2%80%9CMaster%20coding%20skills%20or%20do%20a%20robotics%20project%20as%20these%20are%20going%20to%20be%20used%20in%20space%20technologies%20being%20developed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComplete%20research%20projects%20in%20well-known%20institutes%20and%20develop%20expertise%20in%20an%20area%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENetwork%2C%20Network%2C%20Network.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETry%20to%20build%20a%20professional%20network%20as%20early%20as%20possible%20by%20attending%20conferences%2C%20workshops%2C%20professional%20seminars%20and%20talks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20are%20any%20talks%20in%20planetariums%20or%20research%20institutes%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20attend%20them.%20You%20can%20ask%20questions%20to%20people%20who%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20what%20you%20want%20to.%20You%20could%20find%20a%20mentor%20or%20it%20will%20at%20least%20help%20you%20chart%20your%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Akshata%20Krishnamurthy%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715610103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F1715219850.743726-min-1715319952.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349546%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Akshata