%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Suma%20and%20Rohit%20opted%20for%20roof-based%20rainwater%20harvesting%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20their%202%2C000%20sq%20ft%20home%20in%202020.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20water%20requirements%20are%20currently%20met%20through%20the%20Cauvery%20river%20(60%20percent)%20and%20groundwater%20resources%20(40%20percent).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20learn%20more%20about%20their%20water%20conservation%20efforts%20from%20Rohit%20and%20Suma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20every%20drop%20count%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuma%20grew%20up%20in%20South%20Bengaluru%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20conservation%20and%20sustainable%20living%20were%20very%20much%20part%20of%20her%20day-to-day%20life.%20Around%2020%20years%20back%20when%20groundwater%20recharging%20and%20solar%20panels%20were%20not%20mandatory%2C%20her%20father%20had%20a%20self-designed%20rainwater%20harvesting%20(RWH)%20setup%20installed%20in%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20Suma%20and%20Rohit%20decided%20to%20build%20their%20dream%20home%2C%20they%20aspired%20to%20create%20an%20environmentally%20friendly%20home%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20inspired%20by%20their%20son%E2%80%99s%20school%2C%20designed%20by%20Chitra%20Viswanath.%20They%20were%20also%20inspired%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F181796%2Fbengaluru-couple-sustainable-home-rain-water-harvesting-save-water-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Better%20India%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20highlighted%20Chitra%20and%20her%20husband%20S%20Vishwanath%E2%80%99s%20work%20for%20sustainable%20homes.%20So%20Suma%20and%20Rohit%20decided%20to%20prioritise%20water%20conservation%20initiatives%20when%20they%20built%20their%20own%20home%20in%20Royal%20Placid%20Layout%2C%20Haralur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EProspective%20homeowners%20who%20haven't%20started%20construction%20should%20also%20invest%20in%20an%20underground%20sump%20for%20harvesting%20rainwater.%20There%20is%20no%20silver%20bullet%20to%20solve%20water%20crises%20entirely.%20This%20will%20afford%20you%20more%20than%20a%20decent%20level%20of%20self-sufficiency.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7hk2trq1Pf%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7hk2trq1Pf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20rohitmalekar.eth%20(%40RohitMalekar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRohitMalekar%2Fstatus%2F1769432478224175571%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20their%20neighbours%20rely%20on%20drying%20borewells%2C%20Suma%20and%20Rohit%20opted%20for%20roof-based%20rainwater%20harvesting%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20their%202%2C000%20sq%20ft%20home%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20learnt%20that%20even%20borewells%20as%20deep%20as%201%2C000%20feet%20in%20our%20locality%20went%20dry%20over%20time.%20This%20was%20the%20reason%20we%20chose%20not%20to%20drill%20a%20borewell.%20Besides%2C%20we%20still%20depend%20on%20water%20tankers%20as%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20supply%20is%20insufficient.%20This%20dependency%20increases%20during%20summer%20with%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20supply%20reducing%20to%20one-fourth%20of%20its%20usual%20quantity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20harvest%20rainwater%20for%20non-potable%20purposes%20like%20cleaning%2C%20bathing%2C%20and%