20school%20eschews%20traditional%20grading%20systems%20in%20favour%20of%20levels.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20I%20might%20be%20at%20Level%204%20for%20Gujarati%20but%20Level%208%20for%20math.%20Age%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20determining%20factor%20here%3B%20what%20truly%20matters%20is%20your%20willingness%20to%20learn%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ishita%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshita%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%2097%20children%20residing%20in%20the%20hostel%20provided%20by%20the%20Pathshala%20Foundation.%20The%20majority%20of%20them%20hail%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326013%2Fbengaluru-friends-run-gubacchi-non-profit-to-educate-migrant-worker-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20migrant%20worker%20families%20%3C%2Fa%3Eunable%20to%20afford%20quality%20education.%20Thanks%20to%20Juin%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20these%20children%20now%20have%20access%20to%20opportunities%20for%20a%20brighter%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20just%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Pathshala%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(school)%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathshala%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%20a%20decade%20ago%20as%20a%20mobile%20initiative%20providing%20free%20education.%20Juin%20elaborates%20on%20the%20inception%20of%20this%20initiative%20and%20recounts%20her%20decade-long%20endeavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20a%20bunch%20of%20chatty%20ladies%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Juin%2C%20recalling%202013%2C%20when%20the%20idea%20first%20came%20to%20her.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20school%20teacher%20back%20then%20and%20would%20get%20together%20with%20some%20friends%20from%20my%20community%20to%20have%20raving%20discussions%20about%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20of%20friends%20Juin%20refers%20to%20was%20a%20mix%20of%20teachers%20and%20other%20professionals%20