20my%20education%20at%20Pathshala.%20Once%20I%20completed%20my%20boards%2C%20they%20helped%20me%20get%20admitted%20into%20ITI%2C%20and%20I%20still%20visit%20the%20hostel.%20It%20feels%20like%20home%20to%20me%2C%20and%20I%20keep%20visiting%20the%20children%20on%20various%20occasions%20like%20festivals%20and%20school%20functions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20rely%20on%20the%20kindness%20of%20humans%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20only%20seven%20children%20with%20us%20when%20we%20started%2C%20and%20now%2C%20we%20have%20grown%20to%2097%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Juin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20when%20she%20observed%20the%20number%20of%20children%20growing%20in%20the%20hostel%20that%20she%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20a%20bigger%20place.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20had%20around%20one%20and%20a%20half%20lakh%20rupees%20on%20hand%20and%20were%20searching%20for%20funds.%20But%20our%20motivation%20to%20help%20these%20kids%20kept%20us%20going.%20Fortunately%2C%20we%20encountered%20generous%20individuals%20who%20were%20willing%20to%20support%20us.%20The%20person%20who%20rented%20us%20the%20initial%20hostel%20also%20helped%20us%20acquire%20the%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20kindness%20of%20people%20around%20her%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20times%20when%20we%20did%20not%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20construction.%20The%20construction%20leader%20would%20come%20up%20to%20me%20and%20say%20the%20money%20will%20come%2C%20you%20focus%20on%20getting%20the%20building%20constructed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-4-1715240511.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22You%20can%20help%20Juin's%20in%20f